üìö Help Commands (Start Here)
Command	                          Description	                      Example

Get-Help <Command>	              Show help about a command	        Get-Help Get-Process
Get-Help <Command> -Examples	    Show example uses	Get-Help        Get-Service -Examples
Get-Command <pattern>  	          List available cmdlets/functions	Get-Command *Service*
Get-Help <Command> -Online	      Open online help page	            Get-Help Get-Process -Online

üìÇ Filesystem Commands
Command	                    Description	                          Example

Get-ChildItem (gci)	        List files/folders (like ls)	        Get-ChildItem C:\Windows
Set-Location (cd)	          Change current directory	            Set-Location C:\Users
Get-Location (pwd)	        Show current directory	              Get-Location
New-Item	                  Create file or folder	                New-Item -Path C:\Test -ItemType Directory
Remove-Item	                Delete file/folder	                  Remove-Item C:\Test\file.txt
Copy-Item	                  Copy file/folder	                    Copy-Item C:\file.txt D:\backup\
Move-Item	                  Move or rename	                      Move-Item C:\file.txt D:\newfile.txt
Rename-Item	                Rename file or folder	                Rename-Item C:\oldname.txt newname.txt

üîç Searching & Filtering Commands
Command	          Description	                          Example

Select-String	    Search text in files (like grep)	    Select-String -Path *.log -Pattern "error"
Where-Object	    Filter objects by property	         `Get-Process
Get-Command	      Find available cmdlets/functions	    Get-Command *process*

