Command	                        Description	                      Example

Get-ComputerInfo	              Show system summary	              Get-ComputerInfo
Get-CimInstance -ClassName      CPU details	                      Get-CimInstance -ClassName 
Win32_Processor                                                   Win32_Processor
Get-PhysicalDisk	              Physical disk details	            Get-PhysicalDisk
